# {{ display_name }}

Forked from the Reachy Mini conversation app.

Use the `src/{{ app_name }}/profiles/{{ profile_name }}` folder to customize your own app from this template:
- Edit `AGENTS.md`, `SOUL.md`, `FRONT.md`, `TOOLS.md`, and `USER.md`
- Add profile-local tool modules in `tools/`
- Use `config.jsonl` for structured profile settings
- Keep long-lived state in `memory/`, `session/`, `skills/`, and `prompts/`

Do not forget to customize:
- this `README.md` file
- the `index.html` file (Hugging Face Spaces landing page)
- the `src/{{ app_name }}/static/index.html` (the web app parameters page)

The original README from the conversation app is available in `README_OLD.md`.
